Xtento_GridActions

-------------
  CHANGELOG
-------------

===== 1.0.0 =====
 * Initial Release

[...]

===== 1.2.1 =====
 * Rewrote processor model
 * Suppressed error that could show up for not correctly removed/uninstalled shipping methods

===== 1.2.2 =====
 * Unhold order before invoicing/shipping/completing it.

===== 1.2.3 =====
 * Added example to config.xml to show how the modules columns can be moved to the last columns of the grid.

===== 1.2.4 =====
 * Added a couple new actions to (re-)send emails for already created invoices/shipments.

===== 1.2.5 =====
 * Bugfix release

===== 1.2.6 =====
 * Fixed bug in JS that handles grid carriers/tracking numbers

===== 1.2.7 =====
 * Compatibility with Advanced Order Status

===== 1.2.8 =====
 * Compatibility with certain Amasty extensions

===== 1.2.9 =====
 * Updated XtCore
 * Configuration section opened by default
 * Fixed a bug with regards to status changes

===== 1.3.0 =====
 * Fixed a bug that did not count emails resent as order updates

===== 1.4.0 =====
 + Added permissions to ACL so roles can be limited to allow certain operations only

===== 1.5.0 =====
 * Added ability to render carrier/tracking field into one column in the Sales > Order grid

===== 1.6.0 =====
 + Added ability to mass-capture payments for already invoiced orders
 * Several bugfixes

===== 1.6.1 =====
 * Adjusted adminhtml controller to cope with full page caches better

===== 1.6.2 =====
 + Added option to force order status changes

===== 1.6.3 =====
 + Improved compatibility with not properly uninstalled shipping methods

===== 1.7.0 =====
 + Added ability to combine other actions with "Print Shipping Labels" for supported carriers (just like the "Print Shipping Label" mass action)

===== 1.7.1 =====
 + Individual actions can be assigned to roles now properly, this must be done under "Sales > Orders > XTENTO Simplify Bulk Order Processing > Actions", before it was at System and caused the user to be logged into the modules configuration. When updating be sure to add action rights to roles again.

===== 1.7.2 =====
 * Fixed a bug which could lead to the carrier title being the same for all shipped orders in one execution, even though the shipping description is different

===== 1.7.3 =====
 + Added further possible controller_names to the Observer to match more grids

===== 1.7.4 =====
 * Fixed warning that shows up for rewrite check of certain classes (Shipping_Config)

===== 1.7.5 =====
 + Added ability to localize/translate some more strings of the extension
 * Fixed a bug that lead to the carrier/tracking number column HTML being exported into the built-in CSV/Excel XML export functionality of Magento.

===== 1.7.6 =====
 + Added ability to re-send new order email to customer in bulk
 ! Added compatibility for Magento CE 1.9.0.0 / EE 1.14.0.0

===== 1.7.7 =====
 * Various bugfixes and code optimization in license code

===== 1.7.8 =====
 ! Added compatibility for Magento CE 1.9.1.0 / EE 1.14.1.0

===== 1.8.0 =====
 * Fixed code that updates the order status, drop down still showed the old status eventually.

===== 1.8.1 =====
 + Added ability to uncancel order (and its items)

===== 1.8.2 =====
 * Fixed a bug caused by Magento patch SUPEE-6285 that lead to "Access Denied" screens for admins that don't have full access.

===== 1.8.3 =====
 * Fixed a bug that would not send invoice/shipment emails to admins properly if "Don't notify" is selected but admins want to receive these emails.

===== 1.8.4 =====
 * Fixed a bug that could lead to the error message "Order has been deleted in the meantime?" falsely being displayed
 * Fixed a bug that would not allow you to add multiple tracking numbers to existing shipments

===== 1.8.5 =====
 ! Added compatibility for Magento CE 1.9.3.0 / EE 1.14.3.0